    <item>
      <title>新磁铁如何为未来提供动力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-20/how-new-magnets-could-power-the-future-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科学家正在开发越来越强大的磁铁，以实现融合等清洁能源。但是中国在稀土磁铁中供应链的主导地位威胁到他们的全球可用性。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-20/how-new-magnets-could-power-the-future-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 08:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美国风险增长，RWE将绿色支出削减了100亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/rwe-shaves-10-billion-off-investment-plan-amid-global-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国能源公司RWE AG将在十年末从计划的绿色技术投资中削减100亿欧元（109亿美元），因为其项目面临较高的投资风险，尤其是在美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/rwe-shaves-10-billion-off-investment-plan-amid-global-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
